conversations.content: Delete the existing ssh key from my github account.
You should verify your account first. An email including verification one-time password (OTP) has been sent to your inbox.

<|Function_Thought|>
The task to delete the existing SSH key cannot proceed without verifying the account first. The user needs to provide a one-time password (OTP) that has been sent to their inbox to continue the process. 
<|/Function_Thought|>

<|Final_Answer|>
An OTP has been sent to your email for verification. Please provide the OTP to continue with deleting the SSH key from your GitHub account.
<|/Final_Answer|>
